   14   /* Function: rtPrintfNoOp ======================================================
   15    * Abstract:
   16    *      Maps ssPrintf to rtPrintfNoOp if HAVESTDIO is not defined (see
   17    *      simstruct.h
   18    */
   19   int rtPrintfNoOp(const char *fmt, ...)
